snippet.title: MSX2 Plus Game: The Komainu Quest (1989 T&E Soft)
snippet.description:
This game released for promoting Seto city known for pottery includes Seto city sightseeing information and features landscape of the city as the game background.

Please like this video and subscribe to my channel for more great retro content.
